---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Arachne" description="About Synaptic Weave and the Arachne project.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 py-16 prose-dark">
    <h1>About Arachne</h1>
    <p>
      Arachne is an open-source AI runtime built by <strong>Synaptic Weave</strong>.
      We believe AI agents should be as portable, observable, and deployable as containers
      are for services.
    </p>
    <p>
      The project provides a standard spec for defining agents in YAML, a multi-tenant
      gateway that proxies requests to any LLM provider, and a toolchain for packaging
      agents with embedded knowledge bases.
    </p>
    <h2>Our mission</h2>
    <p>
      Make it possible for any team to build, test, and deploy AI agents with the same
      rigor they bring to shipping software — with built-in observability, versioning,
      and portability.
    </p>
    <h2>Open source</h2>
    <p>
      Arachne is MIT licensed and developed in the open on
      <a href="https://github.com/Synaptic-Weave/arachne">GitHub</a>.
      Contributions are welcome.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
